title: 183 - The name is Bond, Jim Bond
description: Today’s episode of The POD kicks off with all the boys back with even a surprise appearance from sales guy Bruce, Foxy, and Pat McAfee as the boys discuss the busy fall work schedule. The boys then jump right into the Pod FOD, which is a folder compiled of all things around the internet. Today’s FOD included the boys break DAHN of an Avengers vs. X-Men clash, the Thrones spin off trailer, a squid game breakDAHN from Billy Tubes, and much much more. Make sure to subscribe to youtube.come/thepodpmi to watch full episodes and don't forget to send your submissions for the Pod FOD to @ThePodPMI on twitter and instagram. We appreciate you rocking with us and we'll see you Wednesday, Cheers.
